rtl.texi: Remove references to NOTE_INSN_SETJMP.

2005-06-01  Ramana Radhakrishnan  <ramana@codito.com>

	* doc/rtl.texi: Remove references to NOTE_INSN_SETJMP.
	Add documentation for REG_SETJMP
